            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Transfer the <strong>marinated</strong> <strong>hake</strong> and <strong>onion</strong> to an <strong>oven-proof dish</strong> with any <strong>remaining curry marinade</strong></p><p>Put the dish in the oven for 12-15 min or until the fish is cooked through and beginning to brown – this is your <strong>curried fish</strong></p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked once it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
