        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>flaked almonds</strong> to a baking tray and put the tray in the oven for 1-2 min or until lightly browned – these are your<strong> toasted almonds</strong></p><p>Tip: Watch them like a hawk to make sure they don’t burn!</p><p>Add the<strong> toasted almonds</strong> to the <strong>drained brown rice </strong>and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>almond rice</strong></p>",
