    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>curried hake</strong> over the <strong>almond rice</strong> with the <strong>chunky salad</strong> to the side</p><p>Drizzle the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>natural yoghurt</strong> over the fish</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
